#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.truncate.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.truncate"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:1 of
msgid "Truncate a Series or DataFrame before and after some index value."
msgstr "在某些索引值之前和之后截断 Series 或 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:3 of
msgid ""
"This is a useful shorthand for boolean indexing based on index values "
"above or below certain thresholds."
msgstr "这是基于索引值高于或低于某些阈值进行布尔索引的有用简写。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:6 of
msgid "Truncate all rows before this index value."
msgstr "在此索引值之前截断所有行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:8 of
msgid "Truncate all rows after this index value."
msgstr "在此索引值之后截断所有行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:10 of
msgid ""
"Axis to truncate. Truncates the index (rows) by default. For `Series` "
"this parameter is unused and defaults to 0."
msgstr "要截断的轴。默认截断索引（行）。对于 `Series`，此参数未使用，默认为 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:13 of
msgid "This parameter is only kept for compatibility with pandas."
msgstr "此参数仅为了与 pandas 兼容而保留。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:16 of
msgid "The truncated Series or DataFrame."
msgstr "截断后的 Series 或 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:22 of
msgid "Select a subset of a DataFrame by label."
msgstr "按标签选择 DataFrame 的子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.iloc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:25 of
msgid "Select a subset of a DataFrame by position."
msgstr "按位置选择 DataFrame 的子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:29 of
msgid ""
"If the index being truncated contains only datetime values, `before` and "
"`after` may be specified as strings instead of Timestamps."
msgstr ""
"如果被截断的索引仅包含日期时间值，则 `before` 和 `after` 可以指定为字符串"
"而不是时间戳。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:34 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:54 of
msgid "The columns of a DataFrame can be truncated."
msgstr "可以截断 DataFrame 的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:64 of
msgid "For Series, only rows can be truncated."
msgstr "对于 Series，只能截断行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:72 of
msgid "The index values in ``truncate`` can be datetimes or string dates."
msgstr "``truncate`` 中的索引值可以是日期时间或字符串日期。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:94 of
msgid ""
"Because the index is a DatetimeIndex containing only dates, we can "
"specify `before` and `after` as strings. They will be coerced to "
"Timestamps before truncation."
msgstr ""
"由于索引是仅包含日期的 DatetimeIndex，我们可以将 `before` 和 `after` 指定"
"为字符串。它们将在截断前被强制转换为时间戳。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.truncate.truncate:106 of
msgid ""
"Note that ``truncate`` assumes a 0 value for any unspecified time "
"component (midnight). This differs from partial string slicing, which "
"returns any partially matching dates."
msgstr ""
"请注意，``truncate`` 对任何未指定的时间组件假定为 0 值（午夜）。这与部分"
"字符串切片不同，后者会返回任何部分匹配的日期。"

